00:15:43,957 --> 00:15:44,717
if I wasn't here,

292
00:15:45,358 --> 00:15:46,277
you could've become

293
00:15:46,277 --> 00:15:47,277
the fish in the net.

294
00:15:48,918 --> 00:15:49,397
The prince

295
00:15:49,878 --> 00:15:51,238
should've believed a slanderous charge

296
00:15:51,238 --> 00:15:52,480
and thought you wanted to kill him.

297
00:15:53,438 --> 00:15:54,277
How do you know?

298
00:15:55,318 --> 00:15:56,157
I met the prince.

299
00:15:57,118 --> 00:15:58,118
His eyes was full of tears

300
00:15:58,277 --> 00:16:00,038
when he saw a bird dying

301
00:16:00,558 --> 00:16:01,358
in the fight for food.

302
00:16:01,918 --> 00:16:02,438
He said

303
00:16:02,717 --> 00:16:04,277
endless greed would
cause a great calamity.

304
00:16:04,558 --> 00:16:05,957
He must have thought of his children.

305
00:16:06,678 --> 00:16:08,757
He also said I would leave
the southern courtyard.

306
00:16:09,837 --> 00:16:10,878
I was banished by you.

307
00:16:10,998 --> 00:16:11,837
I can't leave

308
00:16:11,998 --> 00:16:12,998
without your pardon,

309
00:16:13,837 --> 00:16:14,678
unless...

310
00:16:19,238 --> 00:16:20,680
I can't leave unless
you lose your power

311
00:16:21,238 --> 00:16:22,318
and it isn't up to you anymore.

312
00:16:45,118 --> 00:16:45,837
The prince

313
00:16:45,837 --> 00:16:46,837
should've plotted an ambush.

314
00:16:47,678 --> 00:16:48,277
Leave now.

315
00:16:50,118 --> 00:16:51,637
No, I can't leave the heir.

316
00:16:52,397 --> 00:16:53,678
Are you still thinking about the heir?

317
00:16:53,957 --> 00:16:56,438
The heir has made a mistake,
but I can't let him be framed by others.

318
00:16:58,558 --> 00:16:59,118
He Lianxin.

319
00:17:00,397 --> 00:17:01,077
He Lianxin.

320
00:17:03,438 --> 00:17:04,720
The prince is already suspecting you.

321
00:17:04,998 --> 00:17:05,717
Have you considered

322
00:17:05,717 --> 00:17:06,637
how dangerous it is now?

323
00:17:08,318 --> 00:17:08,918
He Lianxin.

324
00:17:09,477 --> 00:17:11,318
When will you finally believe me?

325
00:17:13,598 --> 00:17:14,078
Seize him!

326
00:17:14,598 --> 00:17:15,120
How dare you!

327
00:17:15,157 --> 00:17:15,838
I'm the heir!

328
00:17:15,838 --> 00:17:16,598
What do you want to do?

329
00:17:19,157 --> 00:17:19,477
You...

330
00:17:20,237 --> 00:17:21,397
I'm the heir!

331
00:17:21,918 --> 00:17:22,757
What do you want to do?

332
00:17:24,277 --> 00:17:25,157
Why do so many of you

333
00:17:25,718 --> 00:17:27,718
ambush at my father's tent?

334
00:17:27,718 --> 00:17:28,798
What is your intention?

335
00:17:29,997 --> 00:17:30,637
Let me go!

336
00:17:34,877 --> 00:17:35,397
Father.

337
00:17:36,237 --> 00:17:36,798
Father!

338
00:17:40,838 --> 00:17:41,357
Father.

339
00:17:42,757 --> 00:17:44,558
They all are my trusted aides.

340
00:17:44,997 --> 00:17:46,117
They are loyal.

341
00:17:46,598 --> 00:17:47,357
As for you,

342
00:17:48,157 --> 00:17:48,997
I want to ask

343
00:17:50,438 --> 00:17:53,918
about your intention
of breaking into my tent at night.

344
00:17:58,798 --> 00:17:59,678
Forgive me.

345
00:18:01,578 --> 00:18:02,280
What are you doing?

346
00:18:16,718 --> 00:18:19,958
As long as Young Master Xin pled for you,

347
00:18:20,838 --> 00:18:23,918
you  would get through this safely.

348
00:18:28,798 --> 00:18:29,477
Father!

349
00:18:29,958 --> 00:18:30,598
That...

350
00:18:30,958 --> 00:18:32,277
That isn't my dagger!

351
00:18:32,558 --> 00:18:33,038
Father.

352
00:18:35,318 --> 00:18:36,718
(When He Yunshuo loses)

353
00:18:36,718 --> 00:18:38,477
(the last vestige of his expectation)

354
00:18:39,157 --> 00:18:41,918
(for his son whom he's loved for years,)

355
00:18:43,198 --> 00:18:44,877
(he won't entrust Quliang)

356
00:18:45,237 --> 00:18:47,517
(and his lifetime promise
made to the Emperor)

357
00:18:47,958 --> 00:18:49,277
(to this son.)

358
00:19:01,838 --> 00:19:02,318
Thank you.

359
00:19:05,198 --> 00:19:05,558
Fine.

360
00:19:07,397 --> 00:19:08,277
You still want to save me,

361
00:19:08,277 --> 00:19:09,260
even after how I treated you.

362
00:19:10,277 --> 00:19:10,718
Why?

363
00:19:14,117 --> 00:19:15,560
You still want to save me after I caused

364
00:19:16,757 --> 00:19:17,760
the death of our child.

365
00:19:19,397 --> 00:19:19,877
Why?

366
00:19:26,438 --> 00:19:27,718
I ruined your marriage

367
00:19:29,318 --> 00:19:30,997
and banished you
to the southern courtyard.

368
00:19:32,678 --> 00:19:33,517
You still saved me.

369
00:19:35,078 --> 00:19:35,558
Why?

370
00:19:37,757 --> 00:19:39,117
Do you really hate me

371
00:19:41,757 --> 00:19:42,640
as much as you say you do

372
00:19:43,757 --> 00:19:44,877
or are you lying to me?

373
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:48,280
♪Inner feelings like clouds♪

374
00:19:48,280 --> 00:19:52,120
♪Would it be out of reach?♪

375
00:19:55,038 --> 00:19:55,880
You're overthinking it.

376
00:19:57,958 --> 00:19:58,757
I helped you

377
00:20:00,318 --> 00:20:01,678
only because of the outcast status thing.

378
00:20:07,678 --> 00:20:08,718
I can retreat

379
00:20:10,838 --> 00:20:11,958
as soon as you're safe.

380
00:20:12,277 --> 00:20:12,918
Once.

381
00:20:14,038 --> 00:20:14,838
Even if it's just once,

382
00:20:18,400 --> 00:20:21,040
♪It melts frost♪

383
00:20:21,040 --> 00:20:23,920
♪Are you fed up? You must
be missing that person♪

384
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:29,880
♪Forget each other? Look at each other♪

385
00:20:30,038 --> 00:20:31,277
have you

386
00:20:34,157 --> 00:20:35,397
ever missed me?

387
00:20:35,540 --> 00:20:43,240
♪Eventually, the entire world
is under longings♪

388
00:20:46,997 --> 00:20:47,637
Young Master!

389
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:49,318
Young Master, where are you?

390
00:20:49,318 --> 00:20:50,277
He Lianxin, I hate you!

391
00:20:51,757 --> 00:20:52,237
Young Master!

392
00:20:56,958 --> 00:20:57,397
Young Master.

393
00:20:58,357 --> 00:20:59,438
You're here.

394
00:20:59,838 --> 00:21:00,718
I'd been looking for you.

395
00:21:01,038 --> 00:21:02,318
I heard something happened to the heir.

396
00:21:02,558 --> 00:21:03,558
I'm very worried about you.

397
00:21:04,117 --> 00:21:04,958
Are you all right?

398
00:21:20,357 --> 00:21:22,838
(He Lianchu didn't abide
by the ancestor's conduct)

399
00:21:23,157 --> 00:21:24,558
(and the prince's teaching.)

400
00:21:25,157 --> 00:21:27,517
(He has lost ability
to handle political affairs.)

401
00:21:28,117 --> 00:21:30,718
(He has lost conduct
that unites the officials.)

402
00:21:31,757 --> 00:21:33,958
(The heir of Prince An)

403
00:21:34,237 --> 00:21:36,718
(mustn't be him.)

404
00:21:37,678 --> 00:21:41,357
(The Emperor grants He Yunshuo's appeal)

405
00:21:41,918 --> 00:21:45,558
(to depose He Lianchu
from the position of the heir)

406
00:21:45,918 --> 00:21:49,157
(and detains him in his mansion.)

407
00:21:58,318 --> 00:21:58,877
Lianxin.

408
00:22:00,397 --> 00:22:01,718
I've punished

409
00:22:01,718 --> 00:22:03,198
everyone who came to plead for him.

410
00:22:04,578 --> 00:22:05,760
Do you still want to plead for him?

411
00:22:10,718 --> 00:22:11,157
Father.

412
00:22:11,798 --> 00:22:13,277
Deposing the heir is an important matter.

413
00:22:14,318 --> 00:22:15,517
Please think twice.

414
00:22:20,718 --> 00:22:22,318
You're close to Lianchu.

415
00:22:24,877 --> 00:22:25,757
I guessed

416
00:22:27,078 --> 00:22:28,438
you would take part in it,

417
00:22:29,997 --> 00:22:30,757
but you didn't.

418
00:22:31,438 --> 00:22:36,718
So this is the only thing
I'm relieved about.

419
00:22:40,718 --> 00:22:41,237
Lianxin.

420
00:22:42,997 --> 00:22:44,798
Don't be another Yuan Baili.

421
00:23:04,277 --> 00:23:04,997
What brings you here?

422
00:23:06,397 --> 00:23:07,558
You told me

423
00:23:08,038 --> 00:23:09,038
you're saved,

424
00:23:09,318 --> 00:23:10,397
thanks to Lian'er.

425
00:23:11,237 --> 00:23:12,438
I'm thankful.

426
00:23:12,918 --> 00:23:13,718
So I came for a visit.

427
00:23:14,877 --> 00:23:15,477
Yes.

428
00:23:16,318 --> 00:23:17,237
It's thanks to her.

429
00:23:18,277 --> 00:23:18,997
Unfortunately,

430
00:23:19,877 --> 00:23:21,277
that's not for saving me.

431
00:23:24,198 --> 00:23:24,838
I don't feel cold.

432
00:23:29,198 --> 00:23:30,637
Lingwei refused to eat just now

433
00:23:30,958 --> 00:23:31,757
and spilled the food.

434
00:23:32,438 --> 00:23:34,157
I asked her whose fault it was.

435
00:23:34,558 --> 00:23:35,637
She said it's Zhihui.

436
00:23:36,337 --> 00:23:38,460
(Shen Jingrong's Daughter, Lingwei (Childhood))
Such a young child

437
00:23:38,460 --> 00:23:39,680
has learnt to speak against her heart

438
00:23:40,157 --> 00:23:41,198
and the heart of an adult

439
00:23:41,438 --> 00:23:42,517
is much more complicated.

440
00:23:42,997 --> 00:23:44,157
Who knows what is really

441
00:23:44,997 --> 00:23:46,078
on an adult's mind?

442
00:23:49,637 --> 00:23:50,517
Forgive me.

443
00:23:52,798 --> 00:23:53,237
Young Master.

444
00:23:54,318 --> 00:23:54,918
On the other day,

445
00:23:55,477 --> 00:23:56,958
Zhiyue gave me something.

446
00:23:57,237 --> 00:23:58,558
She said she found it
at Lianwei House.

447
00:23:59,678 --> 00:24:00,838
It could make you sad.

448
00:24:00,838 --> 00:24:01,678
So

449
00:24:02,318 --> 00:24:03,318
I didn't dare to take it out.

450
00:24:13,117 --> 00:24:14,477
Ms. Lian sewed this handkerchief

451
00:24:15,198 --> 00:24:16,277
for you before she was banished.

452
00:24:17,780 --> 00:24:21,160
(Xin)

453
00:24:22,598 --> 00:24:23,237
(Once.)

454
00:24:23,838 --> 00:24:24,718
(Even if it's just once,)

455
00:24:25,838 --> 00:24:26,838
have you ever missed me?

456
00:24:31,877 --> 00:24:33,637
I recall

457
00:24:35,598 --> 00:24:36,517
the pain you give me

458
00:24:38,038 --> 00:24:39,598
every day

459
00:24:41,318 --> 00:24:43,117
so that I can remind myself

460
00:24:44,198 --> 00:24:45,357
every time.

461
00:24:47,198 --> 00:24:48,198
I'll never forget.

462
00:24:53,237 --> 00:24:55,477
I hate you

463
00:24:57,078 --> 00:24:57,918
every day.

464
00:25:09,918 --> 00:25:10,357
(Girl.)

465
00:25:12,757 --> 00:25:14,477
(Do you really speak
against your heart?)

466
00:25:15,877 --> 00:25:17,477
Since you keep something in your heart,

467
00:25:18,237 --> 00:25:19,958
rather than speculating alone over here,

468
00:25:20,397 --> 00:25:21,798
why don't you go to that person

469
00:25:22,477 --> 00:25:23,678
and ask her directly?

470
00:25:27,877 --> 00:25:29,000
Go to sleep when you're tired.

471
00:25:31,517 --> 00:25:32,198
Ms. Lian.

472
00:25:32,637 --> 00:25:33,757
It's dark.

473
00:25:34,078 --> 00:25:35,117
Rest early.

474
00:25:35,958 --> 00:25:36,718
It's fine.

475
00:25:36,718 --> 00:25:38,277
Just few more stitches to completion.

476
00:25:41,678 --> 00:25:42,277
Who is it?

477
00:25:42,718 --> 00:25:44,997
Mao Da and Mao Er.

478
00:25:49,038 --> 00:25:51,397
It smells great. Is it ready?

479
00:25:51,838 --> 00:25:52,958
It's just done.

480
00:25:52,958 --> 00:25:54,798
It's freshly stewed to warm you up.

481
00:25:56,038 --> 00:25:57,120
Thank you for thinking about me.

482
00:25:57,908 --> 00:25:58,880
You've come at the right time.

483
00:26:01,297 --> 00:26:02,240
These are for the two of you.

484
00:26:02,438 --> 00:26:03,757
What are these?

485
00:26:04,718 --> 00:26:06,318
The mansion received new wool.

486
00:26:06,997 --> 00:26:07,838
The weather gets cold.

487
00:26:08,357 --> 00:26:09,438
You often travel outside.

488
00:26:10,198 --> 00:26:12,117
Wear it close to your body.
It can keep your knees warm.

489
00:26:18,080 --> 00:26:19,040
I'll serve you with the soup.

490
00:26:21,838 --> 00:26:23,798
We...

491
00:26:24,438 --> 00:26:26,438
We lost our parents since we're little.

492
00:26:27,397 --> 00:26:29,157
No one ever treats me

493
00:26:29,558 --> 00:26:30,078
as good

494
00:26:30,718 --> 00:26:31,277
as you.

495
00:26:32,318 --> 00:26:33,237
You're nice to me.

496
00:26:33,637 --> 00:26:35,157
I surely keep you in mind.

497
00:26:37,078 --> 00:26:37,958
That is how people are.

498
00:26:38,318 --> 00:26:39,237
One's family

499
00:26:39,918 --> 00:26:41,517
may not be as close as friends.

500
00:26:42,198 --> 00:26:42,678
Ms. Lian.

501
00:26:43,477 --> 00:26:44,397
Drink it while it's warm.

502
00:26:46,477 --> 00:26:47,558
It smells so great.

503
00:26:55,877 --> 00:26:56,397
Hot.

504
00:26:57,078 --> 00:26:58,038
Blow it before you drink.

505
00:27:00,277 --> 00:27:00,997
Go back.

506
00:27:01,318 --> 00:27:01,838
Go back to rest.

507
00:27:02,918 --> 00:27:03,517
Try it.

508
00:27:12,357 --> 00:27:13,958
Ms. Lian, it smells great.

509
00:27:24,477 --> 00:27:24,997
Ms. Lian.

510
00:27:25,997 --> 00:27:28,838
We're forced to poison you to death.

511
00:27:29,558 --> 00:27:30,357
You mustn't

512
00:27:30,357 --> 00:27:31,757
blame us after you go to hell.

513
00:27:34,397 --> 00:27:35,078
My heart...

514
00:27:39,318 --> 00:27:40,277
She's not dead?

515
00:27:40,558 --> 00:27:41,157
No.

516
00:27:45,117 --> 00:27:46,277
(It's hard not to get suspicious,)

517
00:27:46,718 --> 00:27:47,997
(with your actions just now.)

518
00:27:48,318 --> 00:27:48,798
Hot.

519
00:27:55,997 --> 00:27:57,798
You're so cruel.

520
00:27:58,997 --> 00:28:00,720
Ms. Lian treated you well
over the last two years.

521
00:28:00,958 --> 00:28:02,198
She saved everything for you,

522
00:28:02,580 --> 00:28:04,480
not to mention the monetary reward
during Spring Festival.

523
00:28:04,598 --> 00:28:06,320
She even remembered
to give you auspicious tassels.

524
00:28:06,397 --> 00:28:09,237
She didn't look at the things
sent over by Mr. Lv

525
00:28:09,438 --> 00:28:11,277
and she sewed kneelets for you,

526
00:28:11,798 --> 00:28:12,438
but what about you?

527
00:28:14,558 --> 00:28:15,558
Ms. Lian

528
00:28:15,918 --> 00:28:17,038
shouldn't have been kind to you.

529
00:28:17,277 --> 00:28:17,798
Dongli!

530
00:28:20,877 --> 00:28:21,438
Stop talking.

531
00:28:23,838 --> 00:28:24,318
Ms. Lian.

532
00:28:25,718 --> 00:28:26,637
We know

533
00:28:26,637 --> 00:28:27,678
you're kind to us.

534
00:28:28,558 --> 00:28:29,798
We swore before

535
00:28:29,798 --> 00:28:30,920
that we wouldn't sell you out

536
00:28:30,920 --> 00:28:33,117
no matter how much money was offered,
but this time, it's different.

537
00:28:33,117 --> 00:28:34,237
It has nothing to do with money.

538
00:28:34,637 --> 00:28:35,997
Our lives matter.

539
00:28:36,318 --> 00:28:36,918
Who was it?

540
00:28:37,757 --> 00:28:38,718
Who threatened you?

541
00:28:44,397 --> 00:28:47,198
We swore

542
00:28:47,918 --> 00:28:49,438
we wouldn't sell you out anymore.

543
00:28:49,798 --> 00:28:50,397
Today,

544
00:28:51,277 --> 00:28:53,038
I'll tell you who it is.

545
00:28:53,718 --> 00:28:54,198
He is...

546
00:28:56,237 --> 00:28:56,838
Ma Da!

547
00:28:57,637 --> 00:28:58,078
Ma Da!

548
00:28:58,157 --> 00:28:58,678
Ms. Lian!

549
00:28:59,157 --> 00:28:59,798
Ma Da!

550
00:29:00,558 --> 00:29:01,877
Ma Da, wake up!

551
00:29:02,318 --> 00:29:02,757
Why?

552
00:29:02,980 --> 00:29:04,670
Are you assaulting us
after you failed to poison me?

553
00:29:22,517 --> 00:29:22,997
Mao Er!

554
00:29:33,798 --> 00:29:34,277
Mr. Lv.

555
00:29:37,517 --> 00:29:38,517
Mao Er.

556
00:29:40,277 --> 00:29:43,237
Nan Ruzhen.

557
00:29:48,678 --> 00:29:49,117
Mao Er.

558
00:30:00,918 --> 00:30:01,718
Nan Ruzhen.

559
00:30:04,877 --> 00:30:06,038
Thank you.

560
00:30:07,517 --> 00:30:09,237
Thank you for reminding me.

561
00:30:09,798 --> 00:30:11,397
Although you've escaped this time,

562
00:30:12,037 --> 00:30:13,840
it won't lucky for you
to survive the crisis everytime.

563
00:30:14,877 --> 00:30:15,798
If Nan Ruzhen knows

564
00:30:15,798 --> 00:30:16,880
the assassination failed,

565
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:17,918
she'll go even further.

566
00:30:22,798 --> 00:30:23,678
Dongli and Li Tang.

567
00:30:24,438 --> 00:30:25,038
Yes.

568
00:30:25,477 --> 00:30:26,798
It's time to go back.

569
00:30:33,598 --> 00:30:34,038
Young Master!

570
00:30:34,757 --> 00:30:37,040
Young Master.
We've received an urgent report.

571
00:30:37,237 --> 00:30:39,357
The southern courtyard
was broken in last night.

572
00:30:40,237 --> 00:30:40,918
What about her?

573
00:30:40,958 --> 00:30:41,517
How is she doing?

574
00:30:41,757 --> 00:30:42,718
The details are unclear.

575
00:30:43,357 --> 00:30:44,078
I only heard...

576
00:30:44,997 --> 00:30:45,877
Yes?

577
00:30:46,117 --> 00:30:48,157
I only heard that the robbers
fought with the guards.

578
00:30:48,598 --> 00:30:49,718
They all died.

579
00:30:57,757 --> 00:30:58,198
Girl!

580
00:31:21,318 --> 00:31:22,598
Madam, it's time for the meal.

581
00:31:23,517 --> 00:31:24,318
Not now.

582
00:31:26,157 --> 00:31:27,117
I want to wait for Lianxin.

583
00:31:29,198 --> 00:31:30,198
I want him to see

584
00:31:30,798 --> 00:31:32,198
my best look as soon as he comes back.

585
00:31:34,678 --> 00:31:35,397
Where is my hairpin?

586
00:31:36,958 --> 00:31:38,117
My jade hairpin.

587
00:31:38,117 --> 00:31:38,598
Where is it?

588
00:31:39,038 --> 00:31:40,798
You're wearing it.

589
00:31:44,558 --> 00:31:45,357
My poor memory.

590
00:31:46,397 --> 00:31:46,958
Do I look good?

591
00:31:47,357 --> 00:31:47,877
Yes.

592
00:31:48,078 --> 00:31:49,277
You're a great beauty.

593
00:31:49,277 --> 00:31:50,318
Anything is nice on you.

594
00:31:51,237 --> 00:31:51,718
You're clever.

595
00:31:57,598 --> 00:31:58,997
Ms. Lian has been confused for some time.

596
00:32:00,078 --> 00:32:01,360
She could recognise people at first,

597
00:32:01,718 --> 00:32:04,997
but not anymore
after she was frightened last night.

598
00:32:05,277 --> 00:32:06,237
Why did no one tell me

599
00:32:06,237 --> 00:32:07,718
about what happened?

600
00:32:10,237 --> 00:32:13,038
Ms. Lian was a servant-concubine
who is banished.

601
00:32:13,318 --> 00:32:13,958
No one else

602
00:32:13,958 --> 00:32:15,038
would dare to disturb you.

603
00:32:16,078 --> 00:32:16,838
I'm, however,

604
00:32:16,838 --> 00:32:17,760
thankful to those robbers.

605
00:32:18,198 --> 00:32:19,598
Hadn't they killed anyone at the courtyard,

606
00:32:20,078 --> 00:32:21,517
you wouldn't have appeared.

607
00:32:24,078 --> 00:32:24,757
Ms. Lian.

608
00:32:25,357 --> 00:32:25,718
Ms. Lian.

609
00:32:25,718 --> 00:32:27,400
- Don't catch me.
- Stop running. Be careful.

610
00:32:32,157 --> 00:32:33,157
Su Nanchun?

611
00:32:34,397 --> 00:32:34,877
Let me do it.

612
00:32:36,517 --> 00:32:37,997
Su Nanchun knows how to comb one's hair?

613
00:32:38,237 --> 00:32:40,397
Ms. Lian, it's Young Master Xin.

614
00:32:42,558 --> 00:32:43,237
Leave us.

615
00:32:43,237 --> 00:32:44,038
Not Young Master Xin.

616
00:32:45,517 --> 00:32:46,757
He is Su Nanchun.

617
00:32:49,397 --> 00:32:50,798
Young Master Xin doesn't want me anymore.

618
00:32:51,958 --> 00:32:53,757
He doesn't want me and the child.

619
00:32:58,157 --> 00:32:58,997
Young Master Xin...

620
00:33:00,997 --> 00:33:02,157
Why wouldn't he want you?

621
00:33:03,078 --> 00:33:04,718
He sent Su Nanchun

622
00:33:05,318 --> 00:33:06,198
over to serve,

623
00:33:06,838 --> 00:33:07,718
accompany you,

624
00:33:09,958 --> 00:33:10,877
wash your face

625
00:33:12,477 --> 00:33:13,277
and comb your hair.

626
00:33:16,997 --> 00:33:17,558
Really?

627
00:33:18,517 --> 00:33:19,517
He sent you over?

628
00:33:21,838 --> 00:33:22,397
It's true.

629
00:33:24,198 --> 00:33:24,798
Yes.

630
00:33:27,558 --> 00:33:28,838
He sent me over.

631
00:33:28,990 --> 00:33:31,960
♪They deepen the bind♪

632
00:33:32,637 --> 00:33:33,637
He said

633
00:33:36,038 --> 00:33:37,117
he was sorry

634
00:33:37,798 --> 00:33:38,918
for not coming to see you.

635
00:33:39,598 --> 00:33:40,598
Sometimes,

636
00:33:42,357 --> 00:33:43,918
it's because of his pride.

637
00:33:45,078 --> 00:33:46,517
Sometimes it was jealousy.

638
00:33:49,277 --> 00:33:50,357
He also said

639
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:53,840
♪Deceitful afterglow♪

640
00:33:54,117 --> 00:33:55,718
he felt as if his heart

641
00:33:57,718 --> 00:33:59,038
was cut by a knife

642
00:34:01,237 --> 00:34:02,558
when he saw you

643
00:34:02,558 --> 00:34:03,357
in this situation.

644
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:05,200
♪See you through♪

645
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:09,960
♪Despite twists and turns♪

646
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:13,840
♪The scenery in my life
is plain yet beautiful♪

647
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:15,878
♪Under your propulsion♪

648
00:34:15,878 --> 00:34:16,798
He said

649
00:34:19,277 --> 00:34:20,398
he missed you very much.

650
00:34:23,997 --> 00:34:24,638
How did you

651
00:34:26,717 --> 00:34:27,598
get hurt here?

652
00:34:27,717 --> 00:34:28,620
How did you hurt yourself?

653
00:34:29,798 --> 00:34:30,997
How? Let me see.

654
00:34:32,957 --> 00:34:35,158
It's this. Remove it.

655
00:34:38,277 --> 00:34:39,078
No.

656
00:34:44,398 --> 00:34:44,917
Girl.

657
00:34:46,477 --> 00:34:47,677
It's easy to get hurt now.

658
00:34:49,358 --> 00:34:50,997
Stop wearing jewellery, okay?

659
00:34:51,638 --> 00:34:52,437
No.

660
00:34:52,638 --> 00:34:54,318
Young Master gave this to me.

661
00:35:01,197 --> 00:35:03,078
Please don't take it away,

662
00:35:03,078 --> 00:35:03,957
okay?

663
00:35:17,197 --> 00:35:17,957
Sorry.

664
00:35:28,118 --> 00:35:28,757
Sorry.

665
00:35:45,917 --> 00:35:46,437
Madam.

666
00:35:48,517 --> 00:35:49,558
Young Master Xin has left.

667
00:35:52,158 --> 00:35:52,917
Madam.

668
00:35:55,277 --> 00:35:56,318
He will come.

669
00:35:59,158 --> 00:36:00,558
He still loves me.

670
00:36:05,757 --> 00:36:06,677
He wouldn't

671
00:36:07,917 --> 00:36:09,358
let me wait for nothing.

672
00:36:11,798 --> 00:36:12,757
He also wouldn't

673
00:36:15,477 --> 00:36:17,358
hurt my heart again and again.

674
00:36:24,277 --> 00:36:24,717
Ruhua.

675
00:36:27,598 --> 00:36:28,358
Do you remember

676
00:36:30,237 --> 00:36:34,957
for whom he kept me waiting last time?

677
00:36:42,318 --> 00:36:44,038
Young Master, everything has been loaded.

678
00:36:46,437 --> 00:36:46,917
Set off!

679
00:36:49,080 --> 00:36:52,640
(General Xin's Mansion)

680
00:37:21,280 --> 00:37:22,900
(Baoji Clinic)

681
00:37:45,158 --> 00:37:45,598
Ms. Lian.

682
00:37:46,734 --> 00:37:48,480
Young Master Xin sent Su Nanchun
to pass a message.

683
00:37:48,799 --> 00:37:50,638
He would leave Quliang
on a business trip for a few days.

684
00:37:51,079 --> 00:37:51,960
He might not make it here.

685
00:37:52,959 --> 00:37:54,279
Tell Su Nanchun

686
00:37:54,678 --> 00:37:55,560
I've run out of medicine,

687
00:37:56,198 --> 00:37:57,799
and Young Master may make another trip.

688
00:38:00,559 --> 00:38:00,999
Ms. Lian.

689
00:38:01,759 --> 00:38:02,358
Young Master

690
00:38:02,678 --> 00:38:03,878
can't leave in this case.

691
00:38:04,598 --> 00:38:05,118
I know.

692
00:38:07,918 --> 00:38:08,878
He hasn't been working

693
00:38:09,319 --> 00:38:09,959
for the prince

694
00:38:09,959 --> 00:38:11,239
because of your illness.

695
00:38:12,719 --> 00:38:13,438
I know.

696
00:38:13,678 --> 00:38:14,559
Just do it.

697
00:38:16,759 --> 00:38:17,198
Noted.

698
00:38:28,598 --> 00:38:30,079
After the heir is deposed,

699
00:38:33,039 --> 00:38:34,039
the young masters

700
00:38:34,959 --> 00:38:36,118
are busy working

701
00:38:36,799 --> 00:38:37,799
for the inheritance.

702
00:38:39,559 --> 00:38:41,918
Lianxin and Lianxiu
had the highest hope at first,

703
00:38:42,678 --> 00:38:46,559
but Lianxin has been holding back for you.

704
00:38:47,198 --> 00:38:48,959
Sure. Let Young Master Xiu
have an advantage.

705
00:38:51,918 --> 00:38:53,198
What else could he do?

706
00:38:54,198 --> 00:38:56,598
Lianxiu has won the favour
of half the population in Quliang.

707
00:38:57,198 --> 00:38:58,759
Even the prince and officials

708
00:38:58,959 --> 00:39:00,279
compliment him.

709
00:39:01,198 --> 00:39:01,959
You're wrong.

710
00:39:02,598 --> 00:39:03,678
The prince and officials

711
00:39:04,198 --> 00:39:06,198
won't compliment him simultaneously.

712
00:39:06,438 --> 00:39:07,719
Yao, you...

713
00:39:08,479 --> 00:39:09,598
Lianxin asked to resign again?

714
00:39:09,918 --> 00:39:10,358
Yes.

715
00:39:11,438 --> 00:39:12,880
He wanted to get medicine for Ms. Lian.

716
00:39:13,239 --> 00:39:14,279
He refused to leave Quliang.

717
00:39:19,398 --> 00:39:19,799
Good.

718
00:39:21,118 --> 00:39:21,678
Very well.

719
00:39:23,759 --> 00:39:25,358
I plan to appeal to my father.

720
00:39:27,279 --> 00:39:27,878
Surprisingly,

721
00:39:28,959 --> 00:39:30,878
Lianxin receives the job
coveted by many people

722
00:39:30,878 --> 00:39:31,799
over half a year,

723
00:39:32,279 --> 00:39:33,878
but he let go of it.

724
00:39:35,838 --> 00:39:37,039
Luo Qinglian

725
00:39:37,559 --> 00:39:38,918
got crazy at the right time.

726
00:39:39,638 --> 00:39:40,678
Do you think

727
00:39:41,239 --> 00:39:42,118
that's really great?

728
00:39:43,559 --> 00:39:44,239
The death anniversary

729
00:39:44,239 --> 00:39:45,840
of the late princess consort
is a few days away.

730
00:39:46,239 --> 00:39:47,770
The prince wants
to pay his respects in person.

731
00:39:47,799 --> 00:39:50,918
He'll be accompanied by Young Master Xin
if you aren't in Quliang.

732
00:39:52,719 --> 00:39:53,719
Let it be.

733
00:39:54,638 --> 00:39:55,880
The heir has been deposed anyway.

734
00:39:56,118 --> 00:39:57,040
The late princess consort

735
00:39:57,040 --> 00:39:58,279
isn't as important as before.

736
00:39:59,638 --> 00:40:00,719
Luo Qinglian.

737
00:40:01,198 --> 00:40:03,239
I thought she was
a stumbling block last time.

738
00:40:04,039 --> 00:40:06,198
Surprisingly, she is a ladder to me.

739
00:40:08,479 --> 00:40:08,838
Come on.

740
00:40:09,039 --> 00:40:10,520
Get some fresh air
with me at the garden.

741
00:40:15,158 --> 00:40:16,600
(You've made Young Master Xin stay again.)

742
00:40:17,959 --> 00:40:19,118
Since someone else wants to do it,

743
00:40:19,678 --> 00:40:20,759
I should let him.

744
00:40:20,959 --> 00:40:21,398
Lian'er.

745
00:40:22,878 --> 00:40:24,079
The heir was deposed too soon.

746
00:40:24,719 --> 00:40:26,398
He Lianxin is still fledging.

747
00:40:26,799 --> 00:40:28,198
The foundation he built in hardships

748
00:40:28,878 --> 00:40:29,838
has left with almost nothing

749
00:40:30,118 --> 00:40:31,559
over half the year.

750
00:40:32,319 --> 00:40:33,519
Why do you want to do this?

751
00:40:34,319 --> 00:40:35,479
You'll find out soon.

752
00:40:35,999 --> 00:40:36,918
Success or failure

753
00:40:37,519 --> 00:40:38,438
depends on this time.

754
00:40:42,158 --> 00:40:42,719
(Lian'er.)

755
00:40:43,759 --> 00:40:44,878
(What are you)

756
00:40:45,398 --> 00:40:46,279
(plotting?)

757
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:51,240
(Secondary Courtyard)

758
00:40:52,079 --> 00:40:53,598
Come down, Ms. Lian!

759
00:40:54,279 --> 00:40:54,638
Ms. Lian!

760
00:40:55,079 --> 00:40:56,719
It's no joke if you fall.

761
00:40:57,279 --> 00:40:57,959
What is she doing?

762
00:40:58,678 --> 00:40:59,198
Young Master.

763
00:40:59,398 --> 00:41:00,320
You're here just in time.

764
00:41:01,079 --> 00:41:02,239
Ms. Lian called herself a bird

765
00:41:02,398 --> 00:41:03,838
since she got up in the morning.

766
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,920
She insisted that she should
fly up to the rooftop.

767
00:41:05,920 --> 00:41:06,398
A bird?

768
00:41:07,438 --> 00:41:08,598
She does have many ideas.

769
00:41:08,678 --> 00:41:09,999
Hurry and think of a way.

770
00:41:11,559 --> 00:41:12,279
Fine.

771
00:41:13,438 --> 00:41:13,918
Girl.

772
00:41:14,959 --> 00:41:16,279
You mustn't jump down.

773
00:41:16,519 --> 00:41:17,918
We're birds,

774
00:41:17,918 --> 00:41:19,638
but our wings

775
00:41:19,638 --> 00:41:20,559
aren't as useful

776
00:41:20,559 --> 00:41:21,279
as before.

777
00:41:21,638 --> 00:41:22,559
You can't jump.

778
00:41:23,358 --> 00:41:23,878
We?

779
00:41:25,838 --> 00:41:27,158
Is Su Nanchun a bird too?

780
00:41:40,540 --> 00:41:44,180
♪From the chaotic dust♪

781
00:41:44,180 --> 00:41:46,400
♪Gracefully stepping out♪

782
00:41:47,560 --> 00:41:50,630
♪Only then did I understand
the beauty of the world♪

783
00:41:51,270 --> 00:41:53,660
♪Why, and for what♪

784
00:41:54,610 --> 00:41:57,860
♪Holding pure intentions
in my heart♪

785
00:41:58,230 --> 00:42:01,040
♪Clinging to black and white♪

786
00:42:01,690 --> 00:42:04,520
♪Only then did I realize
that the path is simple♪

787
00:42:05,080 --> 00:42:07,600
♪It is love♪

788
00:42:08,470 --> 00:42:10,070
♪When fate♪

789
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:13,310
♪Surges like deep clouds♪

790
00:42:15,550 --> 00:42:17,320
♪Regardless of♪

791
00:42:17,760 --> 00:42:19,240
♪What experiences may come♪

792
00:42:19,480 --> 00:42:24,160
♪Unable to linger♪

793
00:42:24,670 --> 00:42:26,640
♪Mountains and waves
are insignificant♪

794
00:42:26,640 --> 00:42:29,230
♪My promises to you remain♪

795
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:35,080
♪Unafraid of obstacles
along this worldly path♪

796
00:42:35,380 --> 00:42:37,630
♪Worries are few♪

797
00:42:38,920 --> 00:42:40,750
♪The moon sets, stars scatter,
and mournful sounds ring♪

798
00:42:40,750 --> 00:42:44,490
♪My promises to you remain♪

799
00:42:45,380 --> 00:42:48,420
♪Life after life♪

800
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:52,120
♪Will follow my heart's desires♪

801
00:42:53,920 --> 00:42:55,730
♪Forever unchanged♪
